{
  "__inputs": [],
  "__requires": [
    { "type": "grafana", "id": "grafana", "name": "Grafana", "version": "10.3.0" },
    { "type": "datasource", "id": "loki", "name": "Loki", "version": "1.0.0" },
    { "type": "panel", "id": "timeseries", "name": "Time series", "version": "" },
    { "type": "panel", "id": "stat", "name": "Stat", "version": "" },
    { "type": "panel", "id": "text", "name": "Text", "version": "" }
  ],
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "description": "Pro-Diab HIS MySQL Health — connections, slow queries, replication lag (placeholder cho mysqld_exporter)",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "MySQL Status",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki_prodiab" },
      "description": "PLACEHOLDER — cần thêm mysqld_exporter + Prometheus datasource để có metrics thực",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service=\"prodiab_backend\"} |= \"MySQL\" [5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "MySQL log events/5m",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] } }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "MySQL Error Log Stream",
      "type": "logs",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki_prodiab" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "{service=\"prodiab_mysql\"}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
        "showLabels": true,
        "showTime": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending",
        "wrapLogMessage": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "MySQL Connection Errors (từ backend log)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki_prodiab" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate({service=\"prodiab_backend\"} |~ \"(?i)(connection refused|too many connections|deadlock|mysql error)\" [5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "MySQL conn errors/s",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" },
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10 }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Slow Query Log Stream",
      "type": "logs",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki_prodiab" },
      "description": "Slow queries từ MySQL error log (cần log_slow_queries=ON trong MySQL)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 12 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "{service=\"prodiab_mysql\"} |~ \"(?i)slow query|Query_time\"",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
        "showTime": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Replication Lag (Placeholder)",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 20 },
      "options": {
        "content": "## Replication Lag\n\n**PLACEHOLDER** — Metric này yêu cầu:\n1. Cài `mysqld_exporter` trên MySQL host\n2. Thêm Prometheus datasource vào Grafana\n3. Query: `mysql_slave_status_seconds_behind_master`\n\n**Cài mysqld_exporter:**\n```bash\ndocker run -d --name mysqld_exporter \\\n  -e DATA_SOURCE_NAME=\"exporter:password@(mysql:3306)/\" \\\n  -p 9104:9104 \\\n  prom/mysqld-exporter:v0.15.1\n```",
        "mode": "markdown"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Database Backup Status (last 24h)",
      "type": "logs",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki_prodiab" },
      "description": "Log từ backup-nightly.sh (cần Promtail scrape /var/log/prodiab/backup-nightly.log)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 24 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "{job=\"backup\"}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
        "showTime": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending"
      }
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "1m",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "tags": ["prodiab", "mysql", "database"],
  "time": { "from": "now-24h", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "Asia/Ho_Chi_Minh",
  "title": "Pro-Diab MySQL Health",
  "uid": "prodiab-mysql-health",
  "version": 1
}
